"10 pounds fully-cooked bone-in ham","1 1/2 cups water","1 1/4 cups dark brown sugar, packed","1/3 cup pineapple juice","1/3 cup honey","2 tablespoons Dijon mustard","1 tablespoon orange juice","2 teaspoons orange zest","1/4 teaspoon ground cloves"